  <title>Add a new world clock</title>

  <p>When you add a new city to the world clock, <app>Clocks</app> displays the
  time in that city. The world clock also tells you if it is day or night in
  the city.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">World</gui> button.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">New</gui> button to add a new city to
      the world clock. Alternatively, you could also press
      <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>N</key></keyseq>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Type the name of a city of your choice in the field provided.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Select an appropriate location from the list.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">Add</gui> button to finish.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

